    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka team visit to Geneva",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A delegation led by Minister Ali Sabri will travel to Geneva today to participate in the 51st session of the United Nations Human Rights Council.",
        "According to this, it has been reported that the committee includes External Affairs Minister Ali Sabri, Nidhi Minister Vijayadasa Rajapaksa, Attorney General's Department and Ministry of External Affairs.",
        "It is noteworthy that the 51st session of the United Nations Human Rights Council will be held in Geneva from the 12th to the 7th of October. (a)"
      ],
